1. *Spavam* u svojoj sobi. (I am sleeping in my room.)
2. Ona je izašla iz sobe dok sam *spavao*. (She left the room while I was sleeping.)
3. Moja sestra *spava* u krevetu. (My sister is sleeping in the bed.)
4. Ona često *spava* posle podne. (She often sleeps in the afternoon.)
5. Moji roditelji *spavaju* u spavaćoj sobi. (My parents are sleeping in the bedroom.)
6. *Spavaš* li dovoljno? (Are you sleeping enough?)
7. *Spavala* je cele noći. (She was sleeping all night.)
8. Beba *spava* u krevetu. (The baby is sleeping in the bed.)
9. *Spavao* sam do 8 ujutru. (I was sleeping until 8 in the morning.)
10. Njegov brat *spava* u drugoj sobi. (His brother is sleeping in the other room.)